<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8182387>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Map of Madagascar showing the distribution records of the Blommersia wittei species complex. Only locations confirmed by molecular data are shown." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8182387/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8182391>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Blommersia bara sp. nov. (= B. sp. Ca5) in life. (A,B): Male holotype ZSM 31/2004 (FGZC 47) from Isalo in dorsolateral and ventral view. (C) Individual from Ankarafantsika displaying egg-guarding behavior. (D) Female paratype ZSM 13/2006 from Tsingy de Bemaraha. (E) Additional individual (not clearly referable to a voucher) from Tsingy de Bemaraha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8182391/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8182395>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Audiospectrograms and corresponding oscillograms of advertisement calls of Blommersia bara sp. nov. (= B. sp. Ca5) from two different localities (each showing several calls of a call series)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8182395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8182399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Preserved name-bearing type specimens of Blommersia wittei and Blommersia bara sp. nov. in dorsal and ventral views. Photographs of the B. wittei holotype by RECOLNAT (ANR-11-INBS-0004) / Antoine Fraysse, available from https:// science.mnhn.fr/institution/mnhn/collection/ra/item/1953.60." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8182399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

